title: L'Oreal Paris Magic De-Crease Eyelid Primer, 0.19 Ounces
description: L'Oreal Paris' magic de-crease eyelid primer is specifically designed to address two common concerns of eye shadow users - wear and creasing. Magic de-crease eyelid primer extends the wear of shadow by up to eight hours and prevents shadow from settling into lines and creases. Magic de-crease eyelid primer can be used with a variety of shadow types, including powder, cream or gloss. So, whether you are looking to create a neutral "9 to 5 look" or a dramatic smoky eye that will last the entire night, the first step will always be the same. One universal shade suits all skin tones.
